27:27.080 --> 27:30.410
I really screwed things up for you.

27:31.330 --> 27:33.750
I failed you worse than your old man.

27:33.780 --> 27:35.270
Don't say that.

27:35.310 --> 27:39.450
If I wasn't such a goddamn screwup, I would
have taken more pills and finished the job right.

27:39.500 --> 27:42.820
Why didn't you come to me?

27:42.830 --> 27:44.910
We can fight the feds in court.

27:44.950 --> 27:48.630
They've got enough on me to put
me away for the rest of my life.

28:00.420 --> 28:03.850
What did the feds ask you for?

28:05.430 --> 28:08.730
Everything I've got on you.

28:09.150 --> 28:14.520
