your life running from this man...

29:25.800 --> 29:30.560
or turn yourself in and face
the repercussions of your past.

29:33.080 --> 29:36.280
That's my choice?

29:39.150 --> 29:42.700
I'm sure your decision
will be well considered.

30:03.160 --> 30:07.420
Yeah, I need to see you. Right away.

